        Use a while loop to keep asking until they guess correctly. Use `import random` and `random.randint(1, 100)` to generate the random number.</instructions>
        <expected>Your game should use a while loop, handle user input, provide feedback, and track the number of attempts. Code should be well-organized and include comments.</expected>
